的更强硬的减排措施，且到 2030 年，全球碳排放量必须下降 28% 至 42%，才能达到《巴黎协定》中将全球升温控制在 1.5~2℃的目标。地球首次短暂突破 2℃升温警戒线 联合国发出警告"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-960aa149bec75d457772571b1d7aff11_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/631285465"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I472shOzx8o8KEAMaCTEwMjU2NDUxMyCx8PWqBjAAOBNAGXIJNjMxMjg1NDY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1700676435.833835", "card_id": "Q_630020762", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 29}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "从事什么职业 / 行业的职场人，容易进入「职场心霾」的状态？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/630020762"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I472shOzx8o8KEAMaCTEwMjI4MzE5MSD+uMeqBjAAODVAGnIJNjMwMDIwNzYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1700676435.834146", "card_id": "Q_631208709", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "新房，坐标长沙，建筑面积 140，套内面积 110 平米左右，是适合水机联供还是单独中央空调 + 地暖？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "目前新婚夫妇一对，正常朝九晚五上班，准备明年要小孩，有小孩后会有老人过来。初步了解一位同事建筑面积 90，壁挂炉冬天地暖费用 3000 元左右，考虑是不是水机后期运行费用能低点。后期需要咨询暖通问题，接受为知识付费。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-6f23c0f8910b6a4a9a75651258a58e17_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal